and machine guns.

743
01:37:26,181 --> 01:37:27,842
The task is hopeless.

744
01:37:27,916 --> 01:37:30,407
Then you refuse
the appointment, do you?

745
01:37:33,155 --> 01:37:35,589
No. I accept it with honor.

746
01:37:36,792 --> 01:37:39,488
You two gentlemen know about wars.

747
01:37:39,561 --> 01:37:41,961
What type of weapon
do you recommend?

748
01:37:56,011 --> 01:37:58,571
It seems the Chinese troops are
advancing toward our northern borders.

749
01:37:58,647 --> 01:38:01,172
Where's His Holiness?

750
01:38:01,250 --> 01:38:03,275
The glory of
a British coronation.

751
01:38:03,352 --> 01:38:06,378
Nowhere in the world
is there anything half so wonderful.

752
01:38:06,455 --> 01:38:09,618
Only once or twice in the life of each
one of us comes such a day as this...

753
01:38:09,691 --> 01:38:12,353
when we know that we are watchlng
history in the making...

754
01:38:12,428 --> 01:38:16,296
when we know that generations to come
will look back on this day...

755
01:38:16,365 --> 01:38:19,562
for May 12, 1937, wIll be
one of the dates in hlstory...

756
01:38:19,635 --> 01:38:23,196
that schoolchildren will learn about
maybe a thousand years from now.

757
01:38:23,272 --> 01:38:24,864
Every moment
the thrill of excitement--

758
01:38:24,940 --> 01:38:29,468
Do you thlnk someday people will
look at Tibet on the movie screen...

759
01:38:29,545 --> 01:38:31,536
and wonder what happened to us?

760
01:38:31,613 --> 01:38:33,376
The coronation coach moves forward.

761
01:38:33,449 --> 01:38:35,917
I don't know.

762
01:38:35,984 --> 01:38:38,077
Don't you have all the answers?

763
01:38:42,224 --> 01:38:44,192
I don't.

764
01:38:51,500 --> 01:38:55,163
On the same field where Tibetans
traditionally gathered for picnics...

765
01:38:55,237 --> 01:38:57,205
ground was cleared
to build an alrstrip...

766
01:38:57,272 --> 01:39:00,764
so that the plane carrying
three Chinese generals could land.

767
01:39:00,843 --> 01:39:04,438
Nearby, the Tibetan army
practiced its maneuvers.

768
01:39:04,513 --> 01:39:07,243
Some of the soldiers
wear ancient mesh armour.

769
01:39:07,316 --> 01:39:10,752
They bring old muskets
and spears as artillery.

770
01:39:10,819 --> 01:39:16,416
The spectacle of a peace-lovlng nation,
vainly attempting to create a mllitary.

771
01:39:16,492 --> 01:39:19,655
