strike a deeply burled
personal chord.

773
01:39:24,399 --> 01:39:27,095
Echoes of the aggressions
of my own country...

774
01:39:27,169 --> 01:39:30,161
the will to overpower
weaker peoples...

775
01:39:30,239 --> 01:39:33,333
bring shame to me.

776
01:39:33,408 --> 01:39:37,868
I shudder to recall how once long ago
I embraced the same beliefs...

777
01:39:37,946 --> 01:39:40,005
how at one time I was, in fact...

778
01:39:40,082 --> 01:39:44,314
no different from
these intolerant Chinese.

779
01:39:46,054 --> 01:39:48,545
The Tibetans say an enemy
is the greatest teacher...

780
