But, General,
It is our custom.

801
01:43:02,617 --> 01:43:04,551
I can sit down there.

802
01:43:21,436 --> 01:43:24,166
Your Holiness,
this is General Chang Jing Wu...

803
01:43:24,239 --> 01:43:27,572
General Than Gua,
General Than Gua San.

804
01:43:27,642 --> 01:43:30,475
They wish to have
an audience with you.

805
01:43:31,913 --> 01:43:35,212
May you have happiness
and prosperity.

806
