is limited.

812
01:44:05,814 --> 01:44:08,408
I am a simple Buddhist monk.

813
01:44:08,483 --> 01:44:13,113
All I know is the scripture
and the words of Lord Buddha.

814
01:44:13,188 --> 01:44:18,353
