01:44:25,467 --> 01:44:27,059
You must understand.

818
01:44:27,135 --> 01:44:31,902
These words are ingrained
in the heart of every Tibetan.

819
01:44:31,973 --> 01:44:37,411
It ls why we are a peaceful people
who reject violence on principle.

820
01:44:39,014 --> 01:44:43,451
I pray you will see this is
our greatest strength...

821
