to surrender.

842
01:50:58,560 --> 01:51:01,495
- But there will be no surrender--
- I said, "Radio Lh asa."

843
01:51:01,563 --> 01:51:04,293
Permission to surrender now.

844
01:51:50,778 --> 01:51:54,407
We lost the war in 11 days,
Heinrich.

845
01:51:54,482 --> 01:51:57,144
This surrender is
our death sentence.

846
01:51:58,486 --> 01:52:03,981
And I'm afraid our friend
Ngawang Jigme has issued it.

847
01:52:04,058 --> 01:52:09,428
He abandoned Chamdo and then
destroyed the ammunition dumps.

848
01:52:10,698 --> 01:52:13,997
Without weapons and ammunition...

849
01:52:14,068 --> 01:52:17,003
there was no hope for
the troops who wanted to fight.

850
01:52:18,339 --> 01:52:21,672
Our guerrillas could have held
the mountain passes for months...

851
01:52:22,577 --> 01:52:24,442
even years.

852
