It would have bought us time to make
appeals for help to other nations.

853
01:52:29,584 --> 01:52:31,950
Now it's lost.

854
01:52:32,020 --> 01:52:34,215
They broke down the gates.

855
01:53:22,603 --> 01:53:24,696
Hello, my friend.

856
01:53:31,612 --> 01:53:33,546
We did what was the best
for our country...

857
01:53:34,649 --> 01:53:36,583
for Tibet.

858
01:53:37,819 --> 01:53:42,222
On the way to Lhasa, I would see
Tibetans wearing these jackets.

859
01:53:42,290 --> 01:53:44,451
"Chinese soldiers.
Very nice.

860
01:53:44,525 --> 01:53:49,053
Glve food, clothes, money.
Very nice."

861
01:53:49,130 --> 01:53:52,759
It's strange to me that something
so harmless as a jacket...

862
01:53:52,834 --> 01:53:56,736
could symbolize
such a great lie.

863
01:54:01,242 --> 01:54:03,972
After all these years, you still
do not understand Tibetan ways.

864
01:54:05,213 --> 01:54:08,774
To return a gift is unforgivable.

865
01:54:11,819 --> 01:54:15,255
A man who betrays his culture
should not preach about its customs.

866
01:54:22,096 --> 01:54:25,031
There was a time
I would have wished you dead...

867
01:54:25,099 --> 01:54:27,294
but your shame
will be your torture.

868
01:54:27,368 --> 01:54:30,804
And your torture
will be your life.

869
01:54:30,872 --> 01:54:33,204
I wish it to be long.

870
01:54:44,986 --> 01:54:47,784
We pray that His Holiness,
the Dalai Lama...

871
01:54:47,855 --> 01:54:51,757
will be granted the power
to unify his people.

872
01:54:51,826 --> 01:54:56,763
We humbly ask the Tibetan government
to honor our request...

873
01:54:56,831 --> 01:55:00,995
and let the Dalai Lama
attain his political majority.

874
01:55:55,590 --> 01:55:58,525
You have the entire palace
in a panlc.

875
01:56:00,495 --> 01:56:03,225
